Package swervelib.simulation.ironmaple.simulation.opponentsim

Class SmartOpponentConfig

java.lang.Object
swervelib.simulation.ironmaple.simulation.opponentsim.SmartOpponentConfig
public class SmartOpponentConfig extends Object
The config is required to make a SmartOpponent. It should throw if configured wrong.
